data.description: This beautifully maintained home has a welcoming presence that is a blend of timeless elegance and modern convenience and is a dream come true. Situated in a prime South Holland location in the Parkside Estates subdivision. This 4-bedroom/3.5-bath home is the perfect fusion of family comfort and entertainment potential with over 3000 square feet of living space plus a finished basement. Step inside this double door entry to this sunlit 2-story foyer where a striking chandelier and wrought iron staircase greet you and your guests. This main level features hardwood floors throughout, a separate dining room, formal living room, half bath, spacious family room with modern fireplace, and an open floorplan with eat-in kitchen, abundance of cabinetry, glass backsplash, granite countertops, and full-size laundry/mud room that leads to your attached 3-car garage. Adjacent to kitchen, the sliding glass patio door leads to a spacious deck and fully fenced backyard and side yard that offers plenty of space for gardening, entertaining, or leisure. Second level features an oversized owner's suite and 3 guests bedrooms with nicely appointed hall bath. The primary suite offers an oasis with its large bedroom, separate sitting room, huge/desirable walk-in closet and spacious spa-like bathroom with jetted tub. The finished basement features open floorplan with its large L-shaped recreation area, and massive bathroom with sauna, a workout room and storage room that has endless possibilities. You won't be disappointed. Schedule your tour today! You'll LOVE it!
